, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She emphasized that her belief in herself, even during the most challenging moments, was crucial to her success.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her belief\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"the most challenging moments\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"her success\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Palesha also expressed that this medal is not just her personal achievement but a victory for the entire nation, and she is confident that Nepal will continue to win more Olympic medals in the future.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7089529174842578e-25, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Palesha\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"this medal\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"her personal achievement\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire nation\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"more Olympic medals\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same event, Coach Kaviraj Negi Lama revealed that while their initial aim was to clinch gold, securing the bronze medal during the repechage rounds was still a remarkable achievement.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaviraj\", \"score\": 0.9999999989663593, \"rank\": 1.0200835510982044e-09, \"text\": \"Kaviraj\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaviraj\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaviraj\"}, {\"begin\":